kku Akbar]] ||\n|-\n| 67 || 2012 || ''[[Bavuttiyude Namathil]]''|| Vanaja ||[[G. S. Vijayan]] || Nominated: [[Filmfare Award for Best Actress]]\n|-\n| 68 || 2013 || ''[[Lokpal (film)|Lokpal]]''|| Dr. Geetha|| [[Joshiy]] ||\n|-\n| 69 || 2013 || ''Players''|| Rose|| Sanal ||\n|-\n| 70 || 2013 || ''[[Breaking News Live]]''|| Nayana ||Sudhir Ambalapaddu ||\n|-\n| 71 || 2013 || ''[[Anchu Sundharikal]]''|| Gauri Lakshmi || [[Aashiq Abu]] ||\n|-\n| 72 || 2015 || ''[[She Taxi (2015 film)|She Taxi]]'' || Devayani (Taxi Driver) || [[Saji Surendran]] ||\n|-\n| 73 || 2016 || ''Aakashvani'' || Vani || Khais Millen ||\n|-\n| 74 || 2016 || ''[[Pinneyum]]'' ||Devi || [[Adoor Gopalakrishnan]] ||\n|-\n|75||2016||''Bhoomikkoru Charamageetham''|| || ||Short film\n|-\n|76||2016|| ''Kaavalal''|| || ||Short film\n|-\n|77||2016||''Kachadhappa''|| || ||Short film\n|-\n\n|}\n\n==Advertisements==\n{{more citations needed|section|date=December 2019}}\n* Nirapara\n* Parachute\n* Vanamala\n* A Geeripai Jewellery\n* Dhathri \n* Dubai Gold and Diamonds\n* V.G.N Jewellers\n* Smartex \n* Kosamattam Gold Loan\n* Shama Spice\n* Alukkas Wedding Center\n* Anashwara Silks\n* Slipons\n\n==Awards==\n;[[Kerala State Film Awards]]\n* 2004: [[Kerala State Film Award for Best Actress]] \u2013 ''[[Perumazhakkalam]]''\n* 2011: [[Kerala State Film Award for Best Actress]] \u2013 ''[[Gaddama]]''\n\n;[[Filmfare Awards South]]\n* 2011:[[Filmfare Award for Best Actress (Malayalam)|Filmfare Best Malayalam Actress Award]] \u2013 [[Gaddama]]<ref>{{cite web\n |url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-07-08/news-interviews/32588512_1_aadukalam-video-pranayam\n |archive-url=https://archive.is/20121204180003/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-07-08/news-interviews/32588512_1_aadukalam-video-pranayam\n |url-status=dead\n |archive-date=4 December 2012\n|title=The 59th Idea Filmfare Awards 2011(South) \n |accessdate=8 July 2012 }}</ref>\n\n;[[Asiavision Awards]]\n* 2013: Best Actress \u2013 Best Actre